'''Wi Kuki Kaa''' ([[16 December|December 16]], [[1938]] - [[19 February|February 19]], [[2006]]), a New Zealand actor, was originally chosen to play [[Ghân-buri-Ghân]] in ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King]]'', but his character did not make the shooting phase.{{Fact}} He does, however, appear as Ghân on the [[The Lord of the Rings Trading Card Game|Decipher card]] "[[LotR TCG: Ghân-buri-Ghân|Ghân-buri-Ghân]]".
